Jika dia tak terima ia esok,

269
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:35,780
dia mungkin akan marah.

270
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:37,380
Jika dia bercakap sesuatu

271
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:39,020
semasa melayani maharaja,

272
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:41,460
puan yang akan kerugian.

273
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:43,140
Terima kasih, Sida-sida Li.

274
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,180
Selamat jalan.

275
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,780
Abang Kai, awak nak laporkan projek.

276
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,860
Perlukah saya ikut sekali?

277
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:52,460
Projek awak

278
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,660
masih ada banyak masalah.

279
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:55,100
Nanti, saya perlu

280
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:56,140
membuat semula untuk awak.

281
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,580
Jika pengarah tak gembira,

282
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,900
saya akan selesaikan untuk awak.

283
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:01,940
Terima kasih, Abang Kai.

284
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:02,460
Pergilah.

285
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,220
Saya pergi dahulu.

286
00:13:06,300 --> 00:13:08,140
Gadis muda ini masih naif.

287
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:17,100
Li Jiakai.

288
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:20,900
Memang awak yang buat ini?

289
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:24,500
Ya.

290
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:25,780
Encik Wu.

291
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,700
Ada apa-apa masalah?

292
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:29,580
Saya akan betulkan sekarang.

293
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:32,220
Bagus. Sungguh kreatif.

294
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:34,740
Saya pandang rendah terhadap awak sebelum ini.

295
00:13:36,740 --> 00:13:37,660
Taklah.

296
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:38,700
Terima kasih

297
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:40,380
kerana menjaga dan mengajar saya.

298
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:41,340
Saya akan beritahu Encik Li

299
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:42,140
tentang hasil awak.

300
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:43,940
Jika projek ini

301
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,420
dilancarkan secara rasmi,

302
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:46,540
kemungkinan besar

303
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:47,820
awak akan bertanggungjawab.

304
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:49,460
Jangan lepaskan peluang ini.

305
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:55,100
Encik Wu, jangan risau.

306
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:55,860
Kali ini,

307
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:57,460
saya akan siapkan tugasan dengan baik.

308
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:58,260
Jangan risau.

309
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:04,940
Encik Wu,

310
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:06,100
kerabat saya

311
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:07,460
hantarkan dua tin teh.

312
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:08,660
Sedap sangat.

313
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:11,380
Saya akan beri awak.

314
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:12,260
Jangan buat begini.

315
00:14:12,780 --> 00:14:14,140
Asalkan awak berkemahiran,

316
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:15,740
peluang itu akan jadi milik awak.

317
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:18,180
Baik. Encik Wu.

318
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:22,580
Encik Wu, saya pergi dahulu.

319
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,060
Sambung kerja awak.

320
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:24,780
Baik.

321
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:28,420
Gundik Zhao, awak menyalin ini?

322
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:31,580
Maharani balu.

323
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:33,860
Semua ini

324
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:35,220
patik salin sendiri.

325
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:38,500
Cantik tulisan awak.

326
00:14:40,740 --> 00:14:42,380
Terima kasih, maharani balu.

327
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:44,740
Mengapa kekurangan ayat terakhir?

328
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:47,340
Maharani balu.

329
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:49,300
Kakak mungkin

330
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,780
rasa bahawa ayat terakhir ini

331
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,420
merupakan ayat terindah

332
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:54,420
semasa menyalin kitab ini.

333
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,220
Jadi, kakak ingin minta maharani balu

334
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,340
menulis ayat terakhir ini.

335
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,940
Gundik Zhao, adakah itu benar?

336
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:02,580
Ya. Memang benar.

337
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:05,060
Bagus.

338
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,780
Apabila saya membaca kitab Buddha,

339
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:09,820
saya paling suka ayat ini.

340
00:15:10,900 --> 00:15:11,740
Gundik Zhao.

341
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:13,540
Awak agak bijak.

342
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:27,020
Tak sesuai.

343
00:15:27,420 --> 00:15:28,660
Maharani balu.

344
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:30,620
Apa

345
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:32,380
yang tak sesuai?

346
00:15:32,820 --> 00:15:34,180
Tulisan awak cantik

347
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,420
dan ia ditulis sekali gus.

348
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:36,780
Jika saya menulis

349
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:38,100
ayat yang terakhir,

350
00:15:38,340 --> 00:15:39,260
ia tak cantik lagi.

351
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:42,060
Gundik Zhao, awak tulislah.

352
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,460
Mengapa awak tak tulis lagi?

353
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:05,540
Saya...

354
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:10,220
Maharani balu.

355
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:11,340
Maharani balu.

356
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:13,180
Tolong saya.

357
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:14,980
Apa yang awak nak cakap?

358
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:17,740
Maharani balu,

359
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:19,900
dia yang menganiayai saya.

360
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:22,220
Inilah tulisannya pada kitab Buddha.

361
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:23,980
Dia menukar ia dengan sengaja.

362
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:25,060
Maharani balu.

363
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:26,100
Maharani balu.

364
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:27,460
Tolong tegakkan keadilan.

365
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:29,260
Gundik He, ada hal sebegini?

366
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:44,580
Mohon maharani balu menyiasat.

367
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:46,500
Tulisan pada kitab Buddha ini

368
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:47,780
bukanlah tulisan saya.

369
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:49,780
Entah mengapa

370
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:50,860
kakak nak cakap begitu.

371
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,740
He Mingyue, awak...

372
00:16:53,860 --> 00:16:54,580
Inilah

373
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:55,660
tulisan dua orang!

374
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:58,780
Awak merosakkan jamuan hari lahir saya,

375
00:16:58,900 --> 00:17:00,260
menyalin kitab tanpa keikhlasan,

376
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:03,020
menganiayai orang lain dan menipu saya!

377
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:05,580
Berani awak buat begini.

378
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:09,460
Mari tarik dia keluar!

379
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:10,500
Masukkannya ke istana sejuk!

380
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:16,820
Abang Kai.

381
00:17:17,140 --> 00:17:18,540
Macam mana? Apa pandangan Encik Wu?

382
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:20,940
Jiaojiao.

383
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,700
Awak kurang pengalaman.

384
00:17:24,860 --> 00:17:26,900
Selepas Encik Wu baca,

385
00:17:28,140 --> 00:17:28,980
dia tak begitu puas hati.

386
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:33,700
Namun, tak mengapa.

387
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:34,860
Nanti,

388
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:36,460
saya buat semula untuk awak

389
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:37,780
dan minta Encik Wu

390
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:38,540
membaca lagi.

391
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:39,900
Terima kasih, Abang Kai.

392
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,180
Namun,

393
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:43,700
saya masih yakin dengan awak.

394
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:46,260
Selepas saya naik pangkat dan gaji,

395
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,020
jawatan saya

396
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:50,260
mungkin akan jadi milik awak.

397
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:53,460
Terima kasih, Abang Kai. Semoga berjaya.

398
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:54,500
Semoga berjaya.

399
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:56,780
Pergilah.

400
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:57,860
Selamat jalan.

401
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:07,140
Dia dipuji dan berpura-pura orang baik.

402
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,940
Dia nak naik pangkat dengan ini?

403
00:18:12,620 --> 00:18:14,340
Harap-harap Li Shu takkan kecewakan saya.

